WEBVTT

01:43.200 --> 01:46.030
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.140 --> 01:49.090
[Episode 9]

04:27.350 --> 04:27.910
Lu Yan!

04:30.230 --> 04:30.830
Lu Yan!

04:35.570 --> 04:36.180
Lu Yan!

04:40.430 --> 04:40.990
Lu Yan!

04:42.520 --> 04:43.150
Lu Yan!

06:06.610 --> 06:07.930
Freeze! Police!

06:35.210 --> 06:35.890
Lu Yan.

06:37.390 --> 06:38.180
Where are you hurt?

06:38.909 --> 06:39.790
Ether.

06:40.150 --> 06:40.790
What?

06:41.980 --> 06:42.780
Ether.

06:44.000 --> 06:44.590
Ether.

06:49.720 --> 06:52.830
[Emergency Department]

06:52.909 --> 06:59.870
[Medical Records Room - Go up to the fourth floor from here]

06:52.990 --> 06:54.150
As for the patient in Bed 32,

06:54.230 --> 06:55.740
you need to pay special attention to his blood pressure.

06:55.870 --> 06:56.710
If anything happens,

06:56.790 --> 06:57.950
let me know immediately.

06:58.030 --> 06:58.830
Okay, I understand.

06:58.870 --> 06:59.510
Matron Qiao,

06:59.510 --> 07:00.350
I'll go up first then.

07:00.430 --> 07:00.830
Go ahead.

07:02.910 --> 07:03.680
Mr. Wen

07:05.280 --> 07:06.160
Why are you here?

07:06.190 --> 07:07.000
Matron Qiao

07:06.250 --> 07:08.530
[Medical Records Room - Go up to the fourth floor from here]

07:07.630 --> 07:08.410
I'm here to look for Lu Yan.

07:08.670 --> 07:09.880
Is Lu Yan in the duty room?

07:10.200 --> 07:11.290
She’s off work.

07:11.430 --> 07:12.160
Off work?

07:13.030 --> 07:14.150
Doesn't she work night shifts?

07:15.190 --> 07:16.080
We just changed

07:16.110 --> 07:17.770
our shift schedule two days ago.

07:17.910 --> 07:18.800
Are you...

07:19.030 --> 07:20.000
looking for Lu Yan for something?

07:22.150 --> 07:22.670
Nothing much.

07:24.670 --> 07:25.460
Doctor.

07:26.310 --> 07:27.310
Lu Yan passed out from being drugged.

07:27.360 --> 07:27.970
Lu.

07:29.190 --> 07:29.800
This way.

07:29.830 --> 07:30.230
Hurry.

07:32.750 --> 07:36.430
[Emergency Department]

07:44.550 --> 07:45.810
Her heartbeat and breathing are normal.

07:45.830 --> 07:46.630
She'll be fine

07:46.670 --> 07:47.470
after taking a rest.

07:48.220 --> 07:49.720
There wouldn't be any after effects, would there?

07:50.380 --> 07:51.159
There wouldn't be.

07:53.390 --> 07:54.690
Then I'll trouble you two

07:54.720 --> 07:55.890
to take care of Lu.

07:55.970 --> 07:56.600
Dr. Wang and I

07:56.630 --> 07:57.510
will take a look at the medical examination report.

07:57.700 --> 07:58.110
Okay.

07:58.210 --> 07:58.560
Okay.

08:07.660 --> 08:08.270
Hello?

08:08.590 --> 08:09.430
Hello, Senior.

08:09.950 --> 08:11.770
We are heading to the crime scene

08:11.970 --> 08:13.460
to see if there are any clues.

08:13.990 --> 08:14.710
Okay.

08:15.120 --> 08:16.570
Let me know if you have any news.

08:36.780 --> 08:37.539
You're awake.

08:41.350 --> 08:41.970
How are you?

08:42.000 --> 08:42.970
Do you still feel dizzy?

08:44.710 --> 08:45.540
Do you feel like vomiting?

08:48.030 --> 08:48.650
Doctor.

08:49.800 --> 08:50.600
She's awake.

08:51.490 --> 08:52.200
Dr. Lu.

08:52.220 --> 08:52.870
You're awake.

08:53.740 --> 08:55.320
Your report is normal.

08:55.350 --> 08:56.440
You'll be fine after some rest.

08:57.300 --> 08:59.300
When can she be discharged?

08:59.630 --> 09:00.730
Once she finished the IV drip

09:00.790 --> 09:02.010
and feels no discomfort,

09:02.040 --> 09:03.000
she can go back.

09:03.350 --> 09:03.790
Alright.

09:05.400 --> 09:05.990
Thank you.

09:06.050 --> 09:07.240
Wait a little longer.

09:07.340 --> 09:08.250
I'll send you home later.

09:09.250 --> 09:10.500
Did you catch him?

09:10.790 --> 09:12.120
Don't worry about that.

09:12.160 --> 09:13.260
We'll definitely catch him.

09:16.820 --> 09:17.890
Close your eyes for a while.

09:21.920 --> 09:24.890
[Huiting Complex]

09:26.550 --> 09:27.720
Slowly, slowly.

09:33.580 --> 09:34.410
Still dizzy?

09:35.620 --> 09:36.940
You guys go home first.

09:38.520 --> 09:39.680
I'll send you in.

09:56.410 --> 09:56.960
You...

09:58.390 --> 09:59.230
You...

10:00.620 --> 10:01.370
You're not leaving?

10:01.570 --> 10:02.700
I'll stay with you outside.

10:02.740 --> 10:03.490
Have a good rest.

10:05.440 --> 10:06.280
Call me if you need anything.

10:06.360 --> 10:07.220
I’m in the living room.

10:08.140 --> 10:09.950
Tang Jie will be here soon.

10:09.990 --> 10:11.320
You guys can go back first.

10:12.270 --> 10:13.440
Let's wait until she comes.

10:14.270 --> 10:15.100
Go to sleep.

10:24.820 --> 10:25.610
You're not leaving?

10:44.300 --> 10:45.650
Leave. Stop looking.

10:47.350 --> 10:48.400
I'm worried

10:48.430 --> 10:49.400
to leave Yan

10:49.430 --> 10:50.230
to someone unrelated to her.

10:51.310 --> 10:52.820
You are the unrelated one.

11:02.110 --> 11:02.720
Mr. Wen.

11:02.940 --> 11:04.570
I’ve bought everything as you ordered.

11:05.830 --> 11:06.300
Okay.

11:07.710 --> 11:08.640
I'm downstairs.

11:08.670 --> 11:09.740
Call me if you need anything.

11:10.150 --> 11:10.990
Okay, thank you.

11:31.230 --> 11:32.030
Go ahead.

11:33.060 --> 11:34.870
There are no surveillance cameras in that alley.

11:34.890 --> 11:35.820
You know that.

11:36.110 --> 11:37.260
But, I've arranged people

11:37.260 --> 11:38.270
to expand the scope

11:38.300 --> 11:39.350
to investigate the stalker.

11:40.030 --> 11:41.030
Lu Yan said

11:41.070 --> 11:42.300
the person used ether.

11:42.870 --> 11:43.900
Investigate this line.

11:44.380 --> 11:45.950
The scene is still under investigation.

11:46.030 --> 11:47.240
But based on the clues

11:47.270 --> 11:47.960
provided by Dr. Lu,

11:48.000 --> 11:49.060
I've also arranged a team

11:49.110 --> 11:50.710
to look into all of the illegal stores

11:50.750 --> 11:53.080
that sell ether.

11:53.230 --> 11:53.780
Senior,

11:53.860 --> 11:55.400
the several cases of rape

11:55.430 --> 11:56.200
and kidnapping women

11:56.230 --> 11:57.030
that we cracked previously

11:57.070 --> 11:57.940
used this too.

11:58.150 --> 11:58.610
Okay.

11:58.630 --> 11:59.670
Let me know if you have any news.

12:11.280 --> 12:12.600
She needs to sleep.

12:12.720 --> 12:13.550
Is it appropriate for you to

12:13.590 --> 12:14.400
create so much noise

12:14.430 --> 12:15.190
in the middle of the night?

12:19.910 --> 12:21.270
I'm afraid she'll be hungry when she wakes up.

12:23.830 --> 12:24.400
Sure.

12:25.350 --> 12:26.560
Then hurry up.

12:26.750 --> 12:27.910
Leave once you're done.

12:28.840 --> 12:29.970
Why aren't you leaving?

12:35.840 --> 12:37.340
Are police officers all so free?

12:37.750 --> 12:38.350
You don't need to work?

12:41.080 --> 12:42.810
Have you found the person who hurt Lu Yan?

12:43.070 --> 12:44.950
Which department do you lead?

12:45.510 --> 12:46.730
So much unnecessary talk.

12:47.470 --> 12:48.550
Mind your own business.

12:59.870 --> 13:00.400
You...

13:01.230 --> 13:02.710
Why are you two still here?

13:04.560 --> 13:05.870
Did the noise wake you up?

13:06.150 --> 13:07.420
Your Senior

13:08.020 --> 13:09.230
is showing off his cooking skills at your house.

13:11.150 --> 13:12.110
Are you hungry?

13:12.270 --> 13:13.230
I made you some porridge.

13:13.720 --> 13:15.230
Thank you for today.

13:15.350 --> 13:16.220
You guys should go home now.

13:16.250 --> 13:17.610
Let me take a rest.

13:19.430 --> 13:20.030
Okay.

13:20.670 --> 13:21.520
Rest assured.

13:21.550 --> 13:22.150
We're leaving.

13:30.630 --> 13:31.660
Don't stay here.

13:32.130 --> 13:32.910
Hurry up.

13:57.510 --> 13:59.090
You even made porridge.

13:59.670 --> 14:00.750
You're all fired up as soon as I'm back,

14:00.750 --> 14:01.310
aren't you?

14:02.180 --> 14:03.830
I've been taking care of her for the past eight years.

14:04.110 --> 14:04.630
I wonder

14:04.670 --> 14:05.870
what you've been doing these eight years.

14:08.830 --> 14:10.520
What feelings do you have for her?

14:14.040 --> 14:15.670
Exactly what you're thinking.

14:17.160 --> 14:18.840
You were kicked out

14:19.240 --> 14:20.450
and you still feel that way?

14:31.510 --> 14:32.170
Jiang.

14:33.820 --> 14:34.760
Why are you two...

14:39.620 --> 14:40.340
I'm leaving.

14:40.690 --> 14:42.110
Goodbye, Wen.

14:46.270 --> 14:47.510
I seem to smell

14:47.530 --> 14:48.740
a strong scent of gunpowder.

14:49.030 --> 14:50.170
Did you two fight?

14:51.200 --> 14:51.950
What are you two doing here?

14:52.220 --> 14:53.620
My wife is here to accompany Lu Yan.

14:53.660 --> 14:54.750
I'm here to accompany my wife.

14:55.080 --> 14:56.760
I told you you don't have to come.

14:57.000 --> 14:58.510
No way, it's so dangerous.

14:58.590 --> 14:59.200
I can't let you

14:59.230 --> 15:00.390
leave my sight by even a bit.

15:02.880 --> 15:03.800
Are you living here?

15:04.620 --> 15:05.310
I'll sleep on the sofa.

15:05.630 --> 15:06.120
Don't worry.

15:06.410 --> 15:08.100
I'll help you protect Lu Yan.

15:09.120 --> 15:09.600
Sure.

15:09.630 --> 15:10.780
Then go upstairs quickly.

15:11.510 --> 15:12.780
Tang Jie,

15:13.070 --> 15:14.100
I'll trouble you

15:14.130 --> 15:15.320
to pay extra attention

15:16.030 --> 15:17.070
and take good care of her.

15:17.420 --> 15:18.110
Don't worry.

15:19.370 --> 15:20.580
Go back and rest.

15:21.740 --> 15:22.600
I'm leaving.

15:26.230 --> 15:26.890
Honey.

15:27.430 --> 15:29.130
Why are they here together?

15:30.030 --> 15:31.120
Right?

15:47.450 --> 15:49.060
[Huiting Complex]

16:37.050 --> 16:38.250
Where are you going?

16:38.610 --> 16:39.370
You're awake.

16:40.150 --> 16:41.780
I have an operation today.

16:42.020 --> 16:43.400
Are you still going to work?

16:43.960 --> 16:45.340
You're indeed this.

16:45.370 --> 16:47.040
The most dedicated and professional employee.

16:47.710 --> 16:48.370
Wait a while.

16:48.770 --> 16:49.920
I'll buy you breakfast.

16:49.950 --> 16:50.510
No, no.

16:50.590 --> 16:51.430
I'll eat in the hospital.

16:51.470 --> 16:52.710
Lie down, lie down.

16:54.120 --> 16:54.990
Look.

16:55.510 --> 16:56.470
Someone

16:56.490 --> 16:57.830
promised to buy us breakfast.

16:57.860 --> 16:59.460
But now he's sleeping like a pig.

16:59.790 --> 17:00.990
He's tired.

17:01.030 --> 17:02.180
Don't see me off.

17:02.310 --> 17:03.500
You two can continue sleeping.

17:03.580 --> 17:04.190
Alright.

17:04.210 --> 17:05.099
I'm going to work.

17:05.119 --> 17:05.980
You two take a rest.

17:06.000 --> 17:07.490
I'll pick you up after work tonight.

17:07.839 --> 17:08.740
No need.

17:08.869 --> 17:09.819
Didn't Jiang Chengyi install a camera

17:09.869 --> 17:10.990
at the gate?

17:11.010 --> 17:11.650
I'm leaving.

17:12.140 --> 17:13.410
Be careful.

17:13.440 --> 17:14.020
Don't worry.

17:14.060 --> 17:14.690
Be careful.

17:21.430 --> 17:22.089
Who is it?

17:22.109 --> 17:22.910
Who is it?

17:22.990 --> 17:24.170
Don't touch my wife!

17:26.900 --> 17:27.599
Honey.

17:27.980 --> 17:28.910
Where is Lu Yan?

17:29.290 --> 17:30.250
She went to work.

17:30.540 --> 17:31.630
You scared me.

17:31.780 --> 17:32.870
Get some more sleep.

17:33.370 --> 17:34.250
-Give me a hug.
-Thank you.

17:36.100 --> 17:38.060
It must be hard to sleep in this spot all night.

17:38.590 --> 17:40.010
Our home is more comfortable.

18:30.320 --> 18:31.070
Morning.

18:31.800 --> 18:32.610
Morning.

18:33.430 --> 18:34.390
You...

18:34.420 --> 18:36.230
Why are you still here?

18:37.260 --> 18:38.780
I'm here....

18:38.970 --> 18:39.750
To...

18:41.010 --> 18:41.900
Execute a mission.

18:43.190 --> 18:44.270
That's so tiring.

18:44.290 --> 18:45.260
What mission?

18:46.110 --> 18:46.790
Well...

18:46.820 --> 18:48.350
W-We have a case here.

18:50.000 --> 18:51.840
Are you okay?

18:53.150 --> 18:54.500
I'm fine. Don't worry.

18:54.780 --> 18:55.400
Okay.

18:55.830 --> 18:56.500
That's good.

18:56.650 --> 18:57.640
I'm going to work.

18:57.680 --> 18:58.170
You...

18:58.260 --> 19:00.280
You can keep waiting here.

19:00.310 --> 19:00.830
Okay.

19:08.370 --> 19:09.140
Let me see you off.

19:11.170 --> 19:12.470
No need.

19:12.850 --> 19:14.620
You didn't sleep well all night.

19:15.560 --> 19:16.570
Keep waiting here.

19:38.310 --> 19:38.850
Hello.

19:38.880 --> 19:39.460
Captain Jiang,

19:39.490 --> 19:40.510
we have a new lead.

19:40.560 --> 19:41.640
Come back to the team soon.

19:41.780 --> 19:42.770
Okay, I'll be right there.

19:50.550 --> 19:51.740
Through our investigation at the crime scene,

19:51.820 --> 19:52.980
we found that

19:53.000 --> 19:53.920
it's indeed ether.

19:54.330 --> 19:55.000
Dr. Lu

19:55.000 --> 19:56.350
is indeed an anesthesiologist.

19:56.370 --> 19:57.950
She told us in advance that they used ether.

19:58.040 --> 19:58.750
She saved us

19:58.750 --> 19:59.590
a lot of time.

19:59.660 --> 20:00.140
Yes.

20:00.160 --> 20:01.560
We have been checking

20:01.590 --> 20:02.630
all of the surveillance cameras

20:02.740 --> 20:03.930
at the areas he could have possibly been to.

20:03.950 --> 20:05.030
Together with our investigative visits,

20:05.050 --> 20:06.030
we've preliminarily identified

20:06.030 --> 20:06.880
this man.

20:07.310 --> 20:08.090
His name is Wang Qiang.

20:08.190 --> 20:09.350
He is 24 years old this year.

20:09.480 --> 20:10.600
He's not a Ninghai local.

20:10.630 --> 20:12.300
His registered residence is in Huozhou.

20:10.670 --> 20:12.130
[Personal information of Wang Qiang]

20:12.550 --> 20:13.160
Unemployed.

20:13.230 --> 20:14.470
A socially idle person.

20:13.820 --> 20:15.490
[Personal information of Wang Qiang]

20:14.750 --> 20:16.030
Wang Qiang went to jail twice.

20:16.270 --> 20:17.510
The first time he was sentenced to two years

20:17.600 --> 20:18.370
for theft.

20:18.820 --> 20:19.830
The second time was

20:19.830 --> 20:21.150
due to infringement of personal information.

20:21.150 --> 20:22.470
The case was very serious.

20:22.560 --> 20:23.590
He was sentenced to a fixed-term imprisonment

20:23.590 --> 20:25.070
of more than three years and less than seven years.

20:25.090 --> 20:26.430
He sells secretly filmed footage?

20:26.450 --> 20:27.140
Yes.

20:26.570 --> 20:32.600
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

20:27.650 --> 20:28.790
Wang Qiang

20:28.980 --> 20:30.180
has many alternative accounts

20:30.990 --> 20:32.590
that are created specially to sell

20:32.650 --> 20:33.590
secretly-taken

20:34.510 --> 20:35.670
photos

20:35.750 --> 20:36.270
and videos

20:36.310 --> 20:37.380
of girls.

20:37.470 --> 20:38.390
But he's very cunning.

20:38.510 --> 20:40.190
He deals with people on foreign websites.

20:40.440 --> 20:41.280
If anything happens,

20:41.310 --> 20:42.900
he deletes his account and disappears.

20:42.940 --> 20:43.940
So, it is quite difficult to deal with.

20:44.670 --> 20:45.550
Where does he live?

20:45.750 --> 20:47.380
We found a rental house.

20:47.430 --> 20:47.950
The landlord said

20:47.950 --> 20:49.340
he hasn't been back for a long time

20:49.400 --> 20:49.870
and also hasn't

20:49.910 --> 20:50.990
paid rent for months.

20:51.230 --> 20:52.290
I guess he's out of money.

20:52.900 --> 20:54.060
We have also checked all hotels,

20:54.410 --> 20:55.000
motels

20:55.030 --> 20:55.640
and hostels

20:55.670 --> 20:56.690
in the city.

20:56.750 --> 20:58.230
There are no registration information of him.

21:00.620 --> 21:02.600
[Personal information of Wang Qiang]

21:04.450 --> 21:05.710
I have a direction.

21:05.730 --> 21:07.240
Doesn't he like taking pictures of girls?

21:07.390 --> 21:08.420
Let's search at places like

21:08.450 --> 21:09.830
universities,

21:10.120 --> 21:11.340
where there are many girls around.

21:11.670 --> 21:12.580
What do you think, Senior?

21:12.840 --> 21:14.650
He must need to find a place to spend the night.

21:15.630 --> 21:17.790
Look for internet cafes

21:17.830 --> 21:18.770
and budget hotels

21:18.950 --> 21:19.820
around his activity area.

21:20.430 --> 21:21.150
See

21:21.180 --> 21:22.610
if he registered using a fake identity.

21:22.670 --> 21:23.110
Got it.

21:23.130 --> 21:23.620
Got it.

21:23.660 --> 21:24.810
Okay, let's go with that.

21:25.050 --> 21:26.150
Time to work.

21:32.010 --> 21:34.450
[Personal information of Wang Qiang]

21:37.410 --> 21:40.590
[69 Lane, Gao'an Road]

22:13.350 --> 22:14.220
Is anyone here?

22:17.180 --> 22:18.590
Sir, do you need to fix your car?

22:23.570 --> 22:28.980
[Daily Goods] [Welcome]

22:26.640 --> 22:28.040
Is this surveillance camera yours?

22:28.140 --> 22:28.930
Yes.

22:29.030 --> 22:30.090
Can I have a look?

22:30.320 --> 22:31.080
Are you crazy?

22:31.110 --> 22:32.190
Not here to fix bikes but to watch my camera footage?

22:32.400 --> 22:33.750
Do you think you're a cop?

22:43.850 --> 22:44.170
[Loading]

22:44.240 --> 22:47.270
[Pay]

22:48.430 --> 22:50.550
You've received 10,000 yuan.

22:52.800 --> 22:54.420
What do you mean?

23:03.370 --> 23:05.460
You've received 10,000 yuan.

23:09.230 --> 23:10.350
Sir, it's inappropriate.

23:10.380 --> 23:11.850
The CCTV footage is private.

23:19.950 --> 23:21.870
You've received 10,000 yuan.

23:24.750 --> 23:26.180
Can I buy this video?

23:26.460 --> 23:27.130
Sir, wait a moment.

23:27.160 --> 23:28.120
I’ll get it for you.

23:47.620 --> 23:48.460
Hello, Mr. Wen.

23:48.650 --> 23:50.550
If someone wants to see me, tell them I’m not here.

23:50.610 --> 23:51.690
Got it, Mr. Wen.

24:34.140 --> 24:35.040
Stop playing with your phone.

24:35.060 --> 24:35.700
Let's eat.

24:42.040 --> 24:42.930
Come on.

24:42.960 --> 24:44.530
Stir-fried beef.

24:44.540 --> 24:45.630
Your favourite.

24:45.770 --> 24:46.560
Let me tell you.

24:46.600 --> 24:47.990
I followed every step

24:48.070 --> 24:49.590
of your stir-fried beef recipe exactly,

24:49.590 --> 24:50.510
but I just can't get the same taste.

24:50.510 --> 24:51.360
I won’t teach you.

24:52.710 --> 24:53.990
It is an exclusive recipe

24:54.010 --> 24:55.050
only my son.

24:55.910 --> 24:57.080
Exclusive recipe.

24:57.110 --> 24:57.990
There's also a soup.

24:58.360 --> 24:59.580
Don't wait for me. Eat it while it's hot.

25:03.120 --> 25:03.890
See?

25:04.550 --> 25:05.510
Your dad

25:05.530 --> 25:07.440
needs to be praised more.

25:07.630 --> 25:08.600
When he is happy,

25:08.620 --> 25:10.480
he'll do all the chores at home.

25:10.850 --> 25:12.560
He even told me about his unique skill.

25:12.750 --> 25:14.200
Do it himself if it's so unique.

25:14.230 --> 25:15.360
What is this called?

25:15.390 --> 25:17.280
The more capable you are, the more you work.

25:19.690 --> 25:21.290
Why am I telling you this?

25:21.630 --> 25:22.520
Later,

25:22.540 --> 25:24.150
I'll teach it to my daughter-in-law.

25:28.510 --> 25:29.730
Tell me.

25:29.990 --> 25:30.590
what is your progress

25:30.590 --> 25:31.790
with Lu?

25:34.190 --> 25:35.190
She's facing some troubles

25:36.150 --> 25:36.950
recently,

25:36.970 --> 25:37.730
so...

25:37.910 --> 25:38.990
We didn't get to talk much.

25:39.010 --> 25:39.970
What is it?

25:43.280 --> 25:44.640
I'll tell you later.

25:46.280 --> 25:48.070
Why are you still sitting here?

25:48.230 --> 25:48.800
If something happened,

25:48.830 --> 25:50.220
you should go and keep her company.

25:50.350 --> 25:51.390
Listen.

25:51.410 --> 25:53.000
girls need company the most

25:53.070 --> 25:54.460
whenever they face problems.

25:54.490 --> 25:55.510
Hurry up and go.

25:56.070 --> 25:57.230
Dad made a whole table of dishes.

25:57.250 --> 25:58.280
It's okay. I'll explain to him.

25:58.310 --> 25:59.100
Go now. Hurry.

25:59.130 --> 26:00.780
There's traffic jam at this hour.

26:00.950 --> 26:01.510
Will this work?

26:01.630 --> 26:02.110
Yes.

26:02.130 --> 26:02.650
Go.

26:03.290 --> 26:03.990
I'll go then.

26:04.030 --> 26:04.590
Hurry up.

26:06.950 --> 26:08.700
-Comfort her well.
-I’m leaving.

26:17.640 --> 26:18.950
Silly girl.

26:21.140 --> 26:22.970
Who closed the door just now?

26:23.280 --> 26:23.990
Son.

26:24.480 --> 26:25.450
Where did he go?

26:26.480 --> 26:28.410
He got a call and went on a mission.

26:30.050 --> 26:31.750
This fellow left just like that,

26:31.830 --> 26:32.590
wasting my effort

26:32.610 --> 26:34.120
to cook so many dishes.

26:34.160 --> 26:34.550
He's so...

26:34.550 --> 26:35.070
You're scolding him now.

26:35.110 --> 26:36.280
Weren't you like this too back then?

26:36.310 --> 26:37.850
Disappeared with just one phone call.

26:37.950 --> 26:39.320
When he had appendicitis,

26:39.390 --> 26:41.070
you didn't come back no matter how much I called.

26:41.150 --> 26:41.910
I carried him

26:41.950 --> 26:43.240
to the hospital alone.

26:43.270 --> 26:43.870
At that time, my back...

26:43.870 --> 26:44.270
Come on.

26:44.290 --> 26:45.010
Eat while it's hot.

26:45.150 --> 26:46.590
My back still has problems from that.

26:46.610 --> 26:47.440
Is it delicious?

26:49.330 --> 26:50.080
Yes.

26:50.870 --> 26:51.640
Do you want to learn?

26:52.470 --> 26:53.510
I'm not teach you.

26:54.560 --> 26:56.480
Come on, eat it while it's hot.

26:57.110 --> 26:57.990
Annoying.

26:58.050 --> 26:59.200
Let me get you some soup.

26:59.550 --> 27:00.230
Come on.

27:00.820 --> 27:03.100
[Emergency]

27:03.200 --> 27:07.740
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

27:14.900 --> 27:16.510
[Access Point]

27:22.130 --> 27:31.260
[Outpatient]

27:40.500 --> 27:43.220
[[Outpatient]]

27:48.300 --> 27:49.160
What are you doing?

27:50.450 --> 27:51.230
I'm just passing by.

27:53.530 --> 27:56.460
Uncle was discharged.

27:56.590 --> 27:57.750
Liu Yuming was discharged too.

27:57.790 --> 27:58.630
You...

27:59.470 --> 28:00.310
Who are you waiting for?

28:03.490 --> 28:04.740
Waiting for a fool.

28:10.650 --> 28:12.090
Who are you calling a fool?

28:14.280 --> 28:15.360
I wanted to see you

28:15.390 --> 28:17.290
but I'm worried you're busy,

28:17.320 --> 28:18.460
so I didn't call

28:18.870 --> 28:19.920
and came directly.

28:20.350 --> 28:21.810
If you need anything,

28:21.840 --> 28:22.800
I'll be here.

28:26.900 --> 28:27.750
You...

28:28.290 --> 28:29.330
How long have you been here?

28:30.230 --> 28:31.480
Not too long.

28:38.650 --> 28:41.480
I brought you some food.

28:41.970 --> 28:43.400
Eat if you got hungry while on duty.

28:51.770 --> 28:52.720
You're hungry already?

28:52.750 --> 28:54.580
Yes, I haven't had dinner.

28:58.150 --> 28:59.040
Have you eaten?

29:00.750 --> 29:01.490
No.

29:23.440 --> 29:24.150
Is it sweet?

29:57.190 --> 29:57.740
Hello.

29:57.990 --> 29:58.560
Captain Jiang.

29:58.590 --> 29:59.860
we’ve located Wang Qiang.

30:00.070 --> 30:00.950
We’ll go there now.

30:01.680 --> 30:02.190
Okay.

30:02.210 --> 30:02.950
Send it to me.

30:03.000 --> 30:03.830
I'll be right there.

30:05.650 --> 30:06.500
Well,

30:06.560 --> 30:07.300
go back first.

30:07.430 --> 30:08.070
I have a mission.

30:08.110 --> 30:08.780
Go ahead.

30:13.650 --> 30:14.460
I'm leaving.

30:58.840 --> 31:00.160
What a crappy place!

31:00.190 --> 31:00.710
It's so narrow.

31:00.730 --> 31:02.140
My car almost got scratched.

31:04.200 --> 31:05.500
Are you dissatisfied?

31:05.620 --> 31:07.080
Move away your hand.

31:08.700 --> 31:09.700
Move away.

31:10.110 --> 31:10.960
How about

31:11.550 --> 31:12.800
we meet at the police station?

31:27.410 --> 31:28.790
This is too little!

31:28.880 --> 31:30.780
Are you bargaining with me?

31:33.300 --> 31:34.600
I got injured.

31:34.630 --> 31:36.070
Isn't it okay to ask for more?

31:36.990 --> 31:37.480
Besides,

31:37.510 --> 31:39.050
there's always a cop following her all the time.

31:39.070 --> 31:40.600
It's too risky for me.

31:40.680 --> 31:41.550
You're only giving this much.

31:41.550 --> 31:42.910
Who's willing to do it?

31:43.070 --> 31:44.740
I'll give you another 50,000 Yuan when the job is done.

31:44.760 --> 31:45.800
Get the job done neatly.

31:47.270 --> 31:48.110
You promised.

31:48.130 --> 31:48.590
50,000.

31:48.590 --> 31:49.740
Not a penny less.

31:53.170 --> 31:54.820
You took so much money from me

31:54.850 --> 31:56.610
and you didn't even take a single photo.

31:57.430 --> 31:58.780
Can you do it or not?

31:59.030 --> 32:00.560
She was lucky last time.

32:02.320 --> 32:03.020
What grudge do you have

32:03.020 --> 32:04.270
against her?

32:04.470 --> 32:05.350
Do you have to do this to her?

32:18.720 --> 32:20.400
Don't ask what you shouldn't ask.

32:22.390 --> 32:24.130
Remember to take more frontal shots.

32:26.150 --> 32:27.510
I want the face to be clear.

32:28.050 --> 32:29.060
I want

32:29.520 --> 32:31.780
her reputation ruined.

32:35.390 --> 32:36.030
But that girl

32:36.050 --> 32:37.360
is quite pretty.

32:37.870 --> 32:38.810
It's a pity

32:39.540 --> 32:40.460
to only take pictures.

32:41.450 --> 32:43.380
If you want to do something with her,

32:43.560 --> 32:44.850
that's your business.

32:44.910 --> 32:45.810
I don't care.

32:46.020 --> 32:47.430
As long as it doesn't involve me.

32:48.800 --> 32:50.320
You really hate her, don't you?

33:08.100 --> 33:08.770
Captain Jiang.

33:13.730 --> 33:14.100
[Please come in for internet access]

33:14.850 --> 33:16.650
[Pisces Internet Cafe]

33:23.320 --> 33:23.980
Where is he?

33:24.580 --> 33:25.490
We won't leak any information.

33:25.530 --> 33:26.160
Only the three of us

33:26.190 --> 33:27.150
are aware of this operation.

33:28.170 --> 33:29.040
Go and ask the front desk.

33:48.320 --> 33:52.460
[Top up your game account and receive a Mimosa VIP membership]

33:53.270 --> 33:54.050
Police investigation.

33:54.670 --> 33:55.880
Where's the guest at computer No. 38?

33:56.200 --> 33:57.190
No. 38?

33:57.550 --> 33:58.550
I didn't see him getting off the computer,

33:58.570 --> 33:59.710
and didn't see him leaving either.

34:00.620 --> 34:01.520
Check the CCTV for me.

34:06.480 --> 34:09.920
[Lobby] [Stairs] [Reception]

34:07.080 --> 34:07.760
Is that him?

34:07.790 --> 34:08.389
Yes.

34:09.199 --> 34:10.000
He left through the back door.

34:10.280 --> 34:10.850
Captain Jiang.

34:10.989 --> 34:11.909
He sneaked out from the back door.

34:12.070 --> 34:12.830
Where is the back door?

34:13.230 --> 34:14.170
Go straight this way.

34:14.310 --> 34:14.810
Let's go.

34:42.179 --> 34:42.710
Yes.

35:01.320 --> 35:02.220
Split up!

35:20.300 --> 35:21.070
Stop!

35:26.220 --> 35:27.050
Stop!

35:33.110 --> 35:35.360
[Energetic Light Meal Alliance]

35:33.950 --> 35:34.550
Excuse me.

35:34.580 --> 35:36.090
Be careful. Make way.

35:49.180 --> 35:49.960
Stop chasing.

35:50.600 --> 35:51.510
Let's go back to the Internet cafe

35:51.510 --> 35:52.430
and search for his personal information.

35:52.910 --> 35:53.360
Okay.

35:56.370 --> 35:59.430
[Energetic Light Meal Alliance]

36:17.810 --> 36:18.740
Who is it?

36:19.700 --> 36:27.350
[Resource Sharing Group 1]

36:20.710 --> 36:21.710
Are there any new ones?

36:21.810 --> 36:23.390
Are there videos of the women's locker room?

36:24.070 --> 36:25.630
The quality is so bad.

36:25.830 --> 36:26.510
So boring.

36:26.550 --> 36:26.990
Refund!

36:28.090 --> 36:29.470
Refund? I can't return a little.

36:29.500 --> 36:30.760
Suit yourself.

36:30.720 --> 36:36.150
[Please don't smoke in bed]

36:57.270 --> 36:58.130
[Rich and handsome]

36:57.730 --> 36:58.720
These women.

36:58.210 --> 37:01.890
[A new hotel I stayed at on a trip. The environment is good.]

36:58.210 --> 37:01.890
[Joy of buying a car hahaha. I'm so cool.]

36:59.110 --> 37:01.300
Sucking up to me once I change my profile picture.

37:01.790 --> 37:03.140
What is this?

37:11.360 --> 37:13.090
Can we get to know each other?

37:19.180 --> 37:20.640
Sure.

37:22.000 --> 37:23.420
Are you in Ninghai?

37:23.830 --> 37:25.780
I'll be on a business trip to Ninghai in a few days.

37:25.950 --> 37:27.970
We can meet if it's convenient for you.

37:29.120 --> 37:30.290
Sure.

37:35.770 --> 37:37.550
This girl is nice.

38:27.400 --> 38:28.030
Hello, young lady.

38:28.060 --> 38:29.040
What would you like to drink?

38:29.640 --> 38:30.860
Ice latte, thanks.

38:30.950 --> 38:31.770
Okay, hold on.

38:48.850 --> 38:49.900
What the hell.

38:50.150 --> 38:52.360
She looks prettier than in photos.

39:19.170 --> 39:20.740
This is quite a beauty.

39:20.740 --> 39:21.230
I'm kneeling.

39:22.000 --> 39:23.460
Can you take a few more photos of her legs?

39:23.520 --> 39:24.950
I love long legs.

39:54.910 --> 39:56.200
Miss, your coffee.

39:57.040 --> 39:57.830
Enjoy.

40:18.130 --> 40:19.360
Can I sit here?

40:23.460 --> 40:24.110
Sure.

40:47.470 --> 40:48.330
What would you like to drink?

40:49.900 --> 40:51.380
I want

40:51.590 --> 40:53.580
to see the photos you took just now.

40:56.190 --> 40:56.760
Sure.

41:08.920 --> 41:10.180
Nice shots.

41:11.960 --> 41:12.560
Wang Qiang.
